<subSubSection pageId="44" pageNumber="45" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="44.[151,1436,1232,1367]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,276,1232,1259]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
Gnathosoma stout, L/W ratio &lt;3.0, in lateral view with distinctly S-shaped ventral margin, not attached to a protrusible tube. Anterior idiosoma without unpaired platelet covering gnathosomal base.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
